1. *Lezi* u krevetu i odmori se. (Lie down in the bed and rest.)
2. Ona je *lezala* na tepihu i čitala knjigu. (She was lying on the carpet and reading a book.)
3. On se *leže* na dečiju postelju. (He lay down on the children's bed.)
4. *Leži* ovde, na stolu je čaj. (Lie here, there is tea on the table.)
5. Ona se *ležala* dok je gledala film. (She was lying while watching the movie.)